- Add TODO.md (backlog) and BUGS.md (defect log) to pair with CLAUDE.md
  as a working system for further development.
- Favorites TV countdown now targets the next season/episode via TMDb
  `next_episode_to_air` instead of the long-past `first_air_date`, so
