Restructure the favorites menu around two app-style bottom tabs while
keeping the Movies/TV split in both:

- Upcoming: the premiere countdown, now limited to titles still to come
  (future or TBA); released titles live in the Watchlist.
- Watchlist: the full library in a catalog-style row (year · runtime ·
  rating), with a single "Sort" menu (release date / rating / runtime /
  title + direction) and optional "group by genre" with section headers.

To support sorting/grouping, favorites now cache genre ids and runtime;
the panel enriches stale movie *and* TV favorites on open (genres,
runtime, TV next-air/status) and resolves genre names via the TMDb
genre lists. Update TODO.md / BUGS.md to match.
